OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start, with early low
OL,6,Fcloud soon burning back to coasts,
OL,7,Fleaving another fine and dry day with
OL,8,Flong sunny spells. Feeling warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine, but cool towards coasts,
OL,10,Fespecially where any low cloud lingers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and sunny evening away
OL,13,Ffrom coasts. Lengthy clear spells
OL,14,Fovernight will allow areas of fog and
OL,15,Flow cloud to develop, with frost
OL,16,Flikely especially in prone rural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
