OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA chilly start once again,
OL,6,Fwith early frost, fog and low cloud
OL,7,Fsoon clearing to leave another dry and
OL,8,Fsunny day. Remaining cooler near
OL,9,Fcoasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,12,Fdry during this period, with some
OL,13,Fsunny spells likely. Risk of overnight
OL,14,Ffog and frost. Often cool near coasts,
OL,15,Fbut warm inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
